{"tid":512971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果正式跪低，發聲明向iPhone用戶致歉","createTime":"2017-12-29T05:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T12:08:41.000Z","uid":73915,"like":8,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"bd97508e78b4d00e1e01efd78e8c540b4e56d894","tid":512971,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T05:21:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.apple.com/hk/iphone-battery-and-performance/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fiphone-battery-and-performance%2F&d=wTNcWpiBTO2ik9uJSyl1EXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=63389e75\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.apple.com/hk/iphone-battery-and-performance/</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果在美國時間 12 月 28 日發表聲明，為近日以 iOS 更新令到舊款 iPhone 性能下降而沒有公開有關機制，向用戶正式道歉。聲明提及蘋果會把非保養期內的更換電池價格下調港幣 407 元 (新價格為港幣 HK$228)，另外還會積極改善使用體驗，包括避免因電池劣化而造成突然關機的現象。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果在 28 日發表的聲明中，指出蘋果發現電池劣化會發生手機突然關機的現象，並說明蘋果如何避免這種情況發生，全部對策都是為了顧客提供最佳的使用體驗。有關應對手法令部份用戶感到失望，蘋果在聲明中向用戶致歉。聲明中蘋果指出「我們從來沒有，亦絕對不會採取任何手段來刻意縮短任何 Apple 產品的壽命，或令使用體驗質素下降，以迫使顧客升級產品」。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果在聲明指了解到顧客憂慮之處，為了重建顧客的信任，釋除對蘋果有關意圖的所有懷疑，蘋果將會實行以下三項措施：<br />\n<br />\n1. 蘋果將會把非保養期內更換電池的價格下調 HK$407，即由 HK$635 減至 HK$228。這個新價格將會在 2018 年 1 月至 12 月，為 iPhone 6 或更新 iPhone 型號主機的用戶提供。<br />\n<br />\n2. 在 2018 年初會在 iOS 軟件更新加入檢查 iPhone 電池狀態的功能，並了解電池狀態是否會影響裝置的效能，提高透明度。<br />\n<br />\n3. 積極改善用戶使用體驗，包括管理效能、避免裝置因電池劣化而造成突然關機的問題。<br />\n<br />\n今次事件的主因是有舊 iPhone 用戶發現在 iOS 升級後主機效能降低，及後有加拿大開發者提供數據證明。及後蘋果在 20 日透過美國媒體，承認有意圖令舊有 iPhone 變慢，原因是他們發現劣化電池會導致 iPhone 突然關機。"},{"pid":"158cadb8d1632b208d997c7ed2548cbdeab8ace6","tid":512971,"uid":138252,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T05:24:43.000Z","msg":"賠錢算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ec1a66a6d919abdb39bd74e71b07a55e203f87","tid":512971,"uid":73915,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T05:25:07.000Z","msg":"換電減價<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f1737aaadf7e8b790e232d0f157ce1aa4e6a9cb","tid":512971,"uid":4917,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T05:27:27.000Z","msg":"都係貴"},{"pid":"c17291449ff32b6bdc28a3629cc8d4d7e9c80d2c","tid":512971,"uid":58413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T05:27:33.000Z","msg":"咁會否整返快部機。"},{"pid":"68cf7dc269b6a6fbbffa9d8d190d3d818842e13c","tid":512971,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c17291449ff32b6bdc28a3629cc8d4d7e9c80d2c","tid":512971,"uid":58413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T05:27:33.000Z","msg":"咁會否整返快部機。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T05:28:24.000Z","msg":"會"},{"pid":"ba9c4106f0208f107908652a3e8a9920d3a03bb0","tid":512971,"uid":6752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T05:29:27.000Z","msg":"換過人地粒舊電呀?"},{"pid":"05bd00371ea63a52a9bbb1bd1c1924b4bed2f0cc","tid":512971,"uid":21392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T05:32:11.000Z","msg":"執柒左去啦"},{"pid":"4a46ac259e1bb39aa3afe843b73c1d7814017309","tid":512971,"uid":26721,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T05:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  銷售手法黎姐 個個衝去換 蘋果又唔知賺幾多 又可宣傳下自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a722e5b42c8cd6eaa794d6c6de2f6545effe99","tid":512971,"uid":4519,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"4a46ac259e1bb39aa3afe843b73c1d7814017309","tid":512971,"uid":26721,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T05:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  銷售手法黎姐 個個衝去換 蘋果又唔知賺幾多 又可宣傳下自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T05:38:0